    "The details are shown in Figs.",
    "3, 4, 5 and 6.When we check the self-attention among various transformer models, the attention in each transformer block changes randomly in FTT models.",
    "However, in our proposed self-attention transformer models, the attention of each transformer block becomes stable in all four datasets.",
    "To avoid possible randomness, we tested our proposed self-attention transformer models in 2 self-attention layers, 4 self-attention layers, 8 self-attention layers, and 12 selfattention layers transformer models.",
